@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Us";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<!-- Title page -->
<section class="bg-img1 txt-center p-lr-15 p-tb-92" style="background-image: url('@Url.Content("~/Content/images/bg-01.jpg")');">
    <h2 class="ltext-105 cl0 txt-center">
        About
    </h2>
</section>

<!-- Content page -->
<section class="bg0 p-t-75 p-b-120">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row p-b-148">
            <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-8">
                <div class="p-t-7 p-r-85 p-r-15-lg p-r-0-md">
                    <h3 class="mtext-111 cl2 p-b-16">
                        Our Story
                    </h3>

                    <p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                        LableStore was founded in the heart of Jordan with a singular vision: to offer high-quality, trusted products to our valued customers. Since our inception, we have been dedicated to curating a collection of items that not only meet the highest standards of quality but also cater to the diverse needs of our clientele. Our journey began with a small team of passionate individuals who shared a common goal of transforming the retail landscape in Jordan by providing a seamless shopping experience.
                    </p>

                    <p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                        Over the years, LableStore has grown into a trusted name in the region, known for our commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction. We have always believed in the power of trust, and that belief drives everything we do. Whether it's sourcing products from the most reputable suppliers or ensuring that our customers receive the best possible service, trust is the cornerstone of our business.
                    </p>

                    <p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                        Our store is more than just a place to shop; it's a community where customers can find products that resonate with their lifestyles, values, and aspirations. We take pride in offering a wide range of items, from fashion and accessories to home goods and electronics, all carefully selected to ensure they meet the high standards that our customers have come to expect from LableStore.
                    </p>

                    <p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                        As we continue to grow, we remain committed to our roots in Jordan, where we strive to support the local economy and contribute to the community. We believe that our success is closely tied to the well-being of the people around us, and we are dedicated to giving back in meaningful ways.
                    </p>

                    <p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                        Any questions? Let us know in-store at 8th floor, 379 Amman St, Jordan, 10018, or call us on (+1) 96 716 6879. Our team is always ready to assist you with any inquiries or support you may need.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-11 col-md-5 col-lg-4 m-lr-auto">
                <div class="how-bor1 ">
                    <div class="hov-img0">
                        <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/images/about-01.jpg")" alt="IMG">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="order-md-2 col-md-7 col-lg-8 p-b-30">
                <div class="p-t-7 p-l-85 p-l-15-lg p-l-0-md">
                    <h3 class="mtext-111 cl2 p-b-16">
                        Our Mission
                    </h3>

                    <p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                        At LableStore, our mission is to build a legacy of trust and quality. We are committed to providing our customers with products that enhance their lives and bring joy to their everyday experiences. We understand that shopping is not just about purchasing items; it's about finding things that make a difference, that reflect who you are, and that bring a sense of satisfaction and fulfillment.
                    </p>

                    <p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                        We are passionate about offering products that are not only stylish and functional but also ethically sourced and produced. In a world where quality and authenticity can sometimes be hard to find, we stand as a beacon of reliability. Our customers know that when they shop with LableStore, they are getting the best that the market has to offer.
                    </p>

                    <p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
                        Our dedication to customer service is unparalleled. We believe that our customers deserve the very best, and we go above and beyond to ensure that their needs are met. From the moment you visit our store, whether online or in person, you will be treated with the respect and care that you deserve. Our team is here to support you at every step of your shopping journey.
                    </p>

                    <div class="bor16 p-l-29 p-b-9 m-t-22">
                        <p class="stext-114 cl6 p-r-40 p-b-11">
                            "Creativity is just connecting things. When you ask creative people how they did something, they feel a little guilty because they didn't really do it, they just saw something. It seemed obvious to them after a while."
                        </p>

                        <span class="stext-111 cl8">
                            - Steve Jobs
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="order-md-1 col-11 col-md-5 col-lg-4 m-lr-auto p-b-30">
                <div class="how-bor2">
                    <div class="hov-img0">
                        <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/images/about-02.jpg")" alt="IMG">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
